    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously preserved by its sole owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic system functions perfectly, and the car comes with a complete, documented service history from the dealership. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on the finest days.",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
